Support for PLA Support for PA/PET

Bed Temperature 35-45°C 80-100°C

Water Soluble No No
Recommended for PLA PA-CF, PA-GF, PET-CF
Cannot be used with PA-CF, PA-GF, PET-CF, ABS, PETG, TPU, ASA PLA, ABS, PETG, TPU, ASA

Kind Reminders
1. Support filament cannot be used to print an item alone, but only to print the supporting portion of that item. AMS is recommended for multi-material printing with Bambu Support filament.
2. Bambu Support filament can only be used with compatible temperatures and filament types. Failure to follow these guidelines can lead to clogs or other issues.

products.title: Bambu Reusable Spool
products.body_html:
Overview: We've built the entire filament feeding system around a reusable spool design and achieved at least 20% less plastic waste in filament consumption. We chose the packaging material carefully to minimize the use of non-recyclable material.

Specification:

  • Materials: ABS
  • Temperature Resistance: ≤70℃
  • Packing Size: 200*200*67 mm
  • Weight: 250g
  • Color: Transparent
